criteria.inclusion_criteria:
1. Partial limbal epithelial stem cell deficiency;
2. Total limbal epithelial stem cell deficiency;
3. Severe symblepharon;
4. Conjunctival sac stenosis.

criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1. Marked ocular surface inflammatory activity;
2. Severe dry eye;
3. Progressive cicatricial disease;
4. Severe ocular surface squamous metaplasia;
5. Pregnant.
